Tested with:
SDK: 2.2.0.v20120907162025
STUDIO: 2.1.3.201209071738
Devices: Samsung galaxy tab(v 2.3.6)


The issue still occurs on android. I am able to reproduce the bug with the given scenario:

An application with app.js with the following code:
{code}

var win1 = Titanium.UI.createWindow({  
    title:'Tab 1',
    backgroundColor:'#fff'
});

require('/_share/info');
		
win1.open();

{code}

and info.js file under _share folder with the following code:

{code}
Ti.API.info('info js called successfully');
{code}

Please find the error logs attached.
